exceptions.tactic: intros f M b a H.
intros f' M b a H.
intros f' M' b a H.
intros f' M' b' a H.
intros f' M' b' a' H.

exceptions.exn: In environment f : R -> R a, b, M : R H : forall x : R, Rmin a b < x < Rmax a b -> f x <= M Unable to unify "match Sup_fct ?M2367 ?M2368 ?M2369 with | Finite y => ?M2367 ?M2370 <= y | p_infty => True | m_infty => False end" with "Sup_fct f a b = Sup_fct f a b".
In environment f : R -> R a, b, M : R H : forall x : R, Rmin a b < x < Rmax a b -> f x <= M Unable to unify "f ?M2367 < M \\/ f ?M2367 = M" with "Sup_fct f a b = Sup_fct f a b".
In environment f : R -> R a, b, M : R H : forall x : R, Rmin a b < x < Rmax a b -> f x <= M Unable to unify "?M2367 /\\ ?M2368" with "Sup_fct f a b = Sup_fct f a b".

original: intros f M b a H. apply Sup_fct_le. intros x Hx. apply H. apply conj. -
